Thanks to all who answered my question.
My batchtest with **/*Test.class failed
because i have put all my classes in sipenum package
which **/*Test.class could not find. I found other way
to filter it out correctly.

I have another question about using fileset :
  if i compile my test cases and put them
in separate directories, how can i build a jar file
that contains all my test cases classes from all my test 
subdirectories.

  for example:
  my test directory output structure looks like this:

    /build/test/gtt/soap/wps
 and
    /build/test/naptr/soap/wps

  All my test cases are in package /soap/wps.

 I compile my test cases and put them in ${build.test.dir}/naptr
${build.test.dir}/gtt subdirectories. 

&lt;target name=&quot;compilenaptr&quot; depends=&quot;compile&quot;&gt;
    &lt;mkdir dir=&quot;${build.test.dir}/naptr&quot;/&gt;
    &lt;javac debug=&quot;true&quot; includeAntRuntime=&quot;yes&quot; srcdir=&quot;${test.dir}&quot;   
destdir=&quot;${build.test.dir}/naptr&quot; &gt;
      &lt;classpath refid=&quot;project.classpath&quot; /&gt;
      &lt;include name=&quot;**/*NAPTR*Test*.java&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;/javac&gt;
  &lt;/target&gt;
&lt;target name=&quot;compilegtt&quot; depends=&quot;compile&quot;&gt;
    &lt;mkdir dir=&quot;${build.test.dir}/gtt&quot;/&gt;
    &lt;javac debug=&quot;true&quot; includeAntRuntime=&quot;yes&quot; srcdir=&quot;${test.dir}&quot; 
destdir=&quot;${build.test.dir}/gtt&quot; &gt;
      &lt;classpath refid=&quot;project.classpath&quot; /&gt;
      &lt;include name=&quot;**/*GTT*Test*.java&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;/javac&gt;
&lt;/target&gt;

  I would like to build a jar file using ant that contains
only /soap/wps/*.classes from both ${build.test.dir}/naptr
and ${build.test.dir}/gtt

  I tried the ant code below but the jar file also pick up
the top level directories /build/test/naptr and
/build/test/gtt which I don&#39;t want. I only want from /soap/wps/
level downward.

&lt;target name=&quot;jar&quot; depends=&quot;compiletests&quot;&gt;
        &lt;mkdir dir=&quot;build/lib&quot;/&gt;
        &lt;jar jarfile=&quot;build/lib/alltest.jar&quot; compress=&quot;true&quot;&gt;
            &lt;fileset dir=&quot;build/test&quot; includes=&quot;**/*.class&quot;/&gt;
        &lt;/jar&gt;
&lt;/target&gt;






